          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἵζω</span></b>  (root <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἑδ</span>), ipf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἷζον</span>, iter. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἵζεσκε</span>:
